Introduction

EPIC TRAVELS also shortened as EPTS is a five member boy group consisting of Ain (former TST, NOM), G.I (former TARGET), Jinhoo (former UP10TION), Sangho (former SNUPER), and Eden (former WeNU, WE:A, and BIGFLO). They released their first single “Closer” on December 3, 2024.

On February 19, 2025 they took to social media to announce a new member, Sangil, former Main Vocalist of Snuper.
